# Python & notebook conventions

- Use type hints where they clarify intent.
- Prefer `ChatGoogleGenerativeAI`, `ChatOllama`, `PromptTemplate`, and LangChain parsers from the existing notebooks as reference.
- In notebooks: one logical step per cell; avoid huge cells; re-run safe (no hardcoded secrets in cells).
- Use `StrOutputParser()` or other LangChain output parsers when building chains.
